Chief Justice Malaba Chronicle Reporter THE Constitutional Court has unanimously confirmed President Emmerson Mnangagwa as the winner of the July 30 Presidential elections. Presenting the judgment to the application by MDC Alliance leader Mr Nelson Chamisa, Chief Justice Luke Malaba said the applicant failed to convince the court of alleged electoral malpractices that he raised in his petition. Meanwhile, the ruling party, Zanu-PF has congratulated Cde Mnangagwa for being duly declared the winner of the polls. WATCH VIDEO OF VERDICT  More to followâ€¦ 